    link: 'handbrake.fr',
  },
  {
    title: 'kinopio',
    description: 'I use this app to map and draft ideas [on a canvas]',
    link: 'kinopio.club',
  },
  {
    title: 'Pandan by @sindresorhus',
    description:
      "This app helps me monitor how long I've been on my PC without taking breaks. It lives in the menu bar.",
    link: 'sindresorhus.com/pandan',
  },
  {
    title: 'Noor',
    description:
      'This is the new workplace communications app built beautifully and tailored to true collaboration. I prefer this to Slack.',
    link: 'noor.to',
  },
  {
    title: 'Rectangle',
    description:
      'This utility helps me to quickly snap and re-arrange windows on my screen.',
    meta: 'Mac only',
    link: 'rectangleapp.com',
  },
  {
    title: 'Medis',
    meta: 'Mac only',
    description:
      "This is a RedisDB GUI client. It's really helpful for someone who's not ready to learn the commands ðŸ˜…. The free trial is good enough.",
    link: 'getmedis.com',
  },
  {
    title: 'Top Notch',
    meta: 'Mac Only',
    description:
      'This app makes your notch vanish and adds some rounded corners at the top corners â€” revealing some cool aesthetics.',
    link: 'topnotch.app',
  },
  {
    title: 'bat',
    meta: 'Shell/terminal app',
    description: 'cat but with syntax highlighting and other cool stuff',
    link: 'github.com/sharkdp/bat',
  },
  {
    title: 'natto',
